6.1424, 326.7572, 325.9445, 325.7015, 326.3895, 326.1495, 325.3576, 326.1829, 324.6116, 324.0212, 323.9706, 323.9861, 324.5697, 324.9757, 323.7654, 323.9788, 324.7118, 324.1825, 323.9813, 323.805, 324.2651, 323.9731, 323.234, 322.7958, 322.6018, 322.9525, 323.1147, 323.6079, 324.0777, 324.7746, 325.2822, 326.4577, 325.8506, 325.6569, 326.7504, 325.5699, 325.3565, 324.6469, 324.3797, 325.1902, 324.3627, 323.8357, 323.9536, 325.4229, 323.3258, 323.9185, 323.3949, 323.5917, 324.0519, 324.6597, 325.2894, 325.1843, 326.0291, 326.5495, 327.3856, 328.2357, 328.7974, 328.1711, 327.8922, 327.3898, 327.0584, 326.2331, 326.2251, 326.5603, 326.7448, 325.6361, 325.1049, 325.4979, 325.0014, 325.8363, 325.7432, 325.1856, 325.0421, 326.0958, 325.6357, 325.3599, 325.47, 324.2812, 323.1403, 323.6596, 323.5894, 322.7258, 322.1739, 323.1079, 323.9524, 323.5304, 323.1143, 323.8454, 323.95, 324.2086, 324.0127, 323.4554, 322.1501, 322.1348, 321.7293, 321.3496, 321.6872, 321.8103, 320.9513, 322.3054, 321.7495, 321.8875, 321.592, 322.1009, 322.1404, 322.212, 322.3011, 322.2424, 323.574, 323.9829, 323.5347, 323.9741, 323.8052, 322.7554, 322.6641, 324.2299, 324.2985, 323.9918, 325.0248, 325.8152, 323.9239, 322.8272, 321.2082, 320.9522, 321.1697, 319.4633, 319.6301, 320.1742, 320.362, 320.222, 320.2639, 320.0072, 319.8084, 319.1368, 319.5125, 319.1618, 319.3755, 319.7806, 320.8621, 319.6897, 319.3548, 319.4529, 319.5533, 320.0921, 319.2817, 320.5761, 319.9681, 320.0337, 321.0538, 320.9346, 322.1279, 322.0141, 323.4012, 322.1289, 322.4903, 322.2862, 321.8007, 320.8291, 321.963, 321.069, 321.0388, 321.6066, 322.4197, 322.4142, 321.8893, 322.2252, 321.8737, 322.2012, 322.5894, 322.0561, 321.7009, 321.7302, 322.3058, 323.0108, 324.4494, 323.4261, 324.0183, 323.8975, 326.6098, 325.5783, 326.8611, 327.5208, 327.6759, 327.2316, 326.6116, 326.1646, 328.8501, 328.8089, 327.3556, 326.0938, 325.5406, 326.4703, 326.09, 325.9346, 326.3147, 325.9645], "summary_html": "<h1>库存水平时序偏离度因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 2.21)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本因子利用商品期货多头库存（inventory_lp）的时序偏离度构建截面多空信号。核心逻辑是：当某品种的库存水平显著偏离其历史均值（以滚动Z-score衡量），市场对该品种的供需定价可能存在偏差。因子在截面上对所有品种的Z-score进行百分位排名，做多库存异常偏高的品种、做空库存异常偏低的品种。</p>\n<p>该因子表现极为稳健：样本内Sharpe 2.21，两个半样本分别为2.79和2.54，时序IC正向品种占比86%，与现有因子库最大相关仅0.40，是一个独立且强劲的基本面截面因子。</p>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{inventory\\_lp}_{i,t} - \\mu_{i}(W)}{\\sigma_{i}(W)}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\mu_{i}(W)</span> 和 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{i}(W)</span> 分别为品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 的 <span class=\"math-tex\">W</span> 日滚动均值和标准差。</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t} = \\text{percentile\\_rank}_{cs}(z_{i,t})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = (\\text{rank}_{i,t} - 0.5) \\times 2 \\in [-1, 1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{direction}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{signal}_{i,t}}{\\sum_j |\\text{signal}_{j,t}|}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = \\text{direction}_{i,t} \\times \\frac{\\text{vol\\_target}}{\\hat{\\sigma}^{\\text{realized}}_{i,t} \\times \\sqrt{252}}</div>\n<h2>参数列表</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认值</th><th>范围</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>zs_window</td><td>100</td><td>63-504</td><td>Z-score 滚动窗口</td></tr><tr><td>hold_days</td><td>1</td><td>1-20</td><td>再平衡周期</td></tr><tr><td>vol_target</td><td>0.10</td><td>0.05-0.30</td><td>年化波动率目标</td></tr><tr><td>inv_field</td><td>inventory_lp</td><td>inventory_lp/ln/sp/sn</td><td>库存字段</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<h3>最优变体</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td><strong>变体名</strong></td><td>inv_lp_zs100_h1_vt10_raw</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Sharpe (扣费后)</strong></td><td><strong><strong>2.21</strong></strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>年化收益</strong></td><td>4.48%</td></tr><tr><td><strong>年化波动率</strong></td><td>2.03%</td></tr><tr><td><strong>最大回撤</strong></td><td>-1.58%</td></tr><tr><td><strong>日均换手率</strong></td><td>6.2%</td></tr><tr><td><strong>覆盖品种</strong></td><td>56</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3>前5变体对比</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>变体</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>年化收益</th><th>最大回撤</th></tr><tr><td>inv_lp_zs100_h1_vt10_raw</td><td>2.21</td><td>4.48%</td><td>-1.58%</td></tr><tr><td>inv_lp_zs150_h1_vt10_raw</td><td>2.19</td><td>4.85%</td><td>-1.47%</td></tr><tr><td>inv_lp_zs126_h1_vt10_raw</td><td>2.14</td><td>4.37%</td><td>-1.47%</td></tr><tr><td>inv_combo_zs126_h5_raw (R2)</td><td>1.94</td><td>6.12%</td><td>-2.32%</td></tr><tr><td>inv_lp_zs126_h5_raw (R1)</td><td>2.00</td><td>6.21%</td><td>-2.32%</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3>信号质量</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>截面IC</td><td>0.0198</td></tr><tr><td>截面ICIR</td><td>0.12</td></tr><tr><td>时序IC</td><td>0.0243</td></tr><tr><td>时序ICIR</td><td>0.76</td></tr><tr><td>IC正向品种占比</td><td>86%</td></tr><tr><td>半样本前半Sharpe</td><td><strong>2.79</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本后半Sharpe</td><td><strong>2.54</strong></td></tr></table></div>\n<h3>与因子库相关性</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>最大相关系数</td><td>0.40</td></tr><tr><td>最相似因子</td><td>xingye_combo_M90_H3</td></tr><tr><td>冗余判定</td><td>marginal (非冗余)</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 2.00)</strong>：初始实现，覆盖基准逻辑（inventory_lp zscore -&gt; rank -&gt; continuous signal -&gt; L1 normalize -&gt; vol_target_scale）。参数网格覆盖 zs_window={126,180,252,504}、hold_days={1,5,10,20}、vol_target={0.10,0.15,0.20}，以及 inventory_sp 和 lp+sp 组合变体。意外发现 zs=126（半年窗口）优于基准的 zs=252，inv_lp_zs126_h5_raw 达到 Sharpe 2.00。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 1.94)</strong>：扩展参数空间（加入 zs=63/90），添加 sym_rolling_ic_gate 过滤弱品种，测试 inventory_ln 字段。R2 最优变体 inv_combo_zs126_h5_raw (Sharpe 1.94) 略低于 R1，但验证了信号在不同库存字段间的稳健性。IC-gate 变体与非 gate 变体持平，说明信号在大多数品种上均有效（77% 品种 IC&gt;0）。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 2.21)</strong>：关键突破。在 zs=100/126/150 范围内做细粒度参数网格，同时覆盖 vol_target={0.10,0.15,0.20} 和 hold_days={1,5}。发现低 vol_target (0.10) 配合 hold=1 显著提升 Sharpe（从 2.00 到 2.21），原因是更保守的波动率目标降低了噪声品种的仓位暴露。新增 inventory_sn (Sharpe 1.64) 和 inventory_21 (Sharpe -0.41) 的对比确认了 inventory_lp 是最佳字段。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>主要字段</strong>: inventory_lp（多头库存，非空率约36%总体，近年&gt;90%）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（56个有库存数据）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每日换仓或5日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 基本面数据（inventory_lp）存在历史NaN，早期品种覆盖率较低\n<p>- 低 vol_target (0.10) 导致绝对收益偏低（年化 4.5%），但风险调整后表现优异 - inventory_21 字段信号为负，不适合此逻辑</p>"}